d filtration media in the form of diatomaceous earth and perlites headquartered in pittsburgh pennsylvania the company employs approximately  people and operates  manufacturing reactivation innovation and equipment fabrication facilities in the us asia and in europe where calgon carbon is known as chemviron for more information about calgon carbons leading activated carbon filtration media and ultraviolet technology solutions visit wwwcalgoncarboncom this news release may contain historical information and forwardlooking statements forwardlooking statements typically contain words such as expect believe estimate anticipate or similar words indicating that future outcomes are uncertain statements looking forward in time are included herein pursuant to the safe harbor provision of the private securities litigation reform act of  they involve known and unknown risks and uncertainties that may cause the companys actual results in future periods to be materially different from any future performance suggested herein any forwardlooking statement speaks only as of the date on which such statement is made and the company does not intend to correct or update any forwardlooking statements whether as a result of new information future events or otherwise unless required to do so by the federal securities laws of the united states view source version on businesswirecom httpwwwbusinesswirecomnewshomeen source calgon carbon corporation calgon carbon corporation dan crookshank director  investor relations  treasurer  dcrookshankcalgoncarboncom calgon carbon corporation published this content on  july  and is solely responsible for the information contained herein distributed by public unedited and unaltered on  july   utc original documenthttpphxcorporateirnetphoenixzhtmlcpirolnewsarticleid public permalinkhttpwwwpublicnowcomviewdcbabacddffbe cartlatest newsall american usc footbal player joseph m boskovich jr now picks all american value stocks for his clientspaul hogan picks tec